        <title>TROUBLESHOOTING</title>
        <table id="t4700104">
            <title>Troubleshooting Chart</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.52in"/>
                <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3.94in"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">APPLICATION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TROUBLESHOOTING SUGGESTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1">
                            <para>Hoses not warm to the touch</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check heater cut-off valves (open) to make sure they are open. Check the butterfly
                                valve for proper operation.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1" morerows="1">
                            <para>Cold air flow from heaters.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check coolant level and hoses for indications of coolant flow.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>-</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check for kinks and air blockage.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1">
                            <para>No air flow from heater</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check blower and motor switch.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1" morerows="1">
                            <para>Blower motor has one speed only.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check wiring and switch connection.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>-</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check the resistor on the motor.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1">
                            <para>Poor water circulation.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Check booster pump and hose routing.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="col1">
                            <para>Air in the heater hose system.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                            <para>Remove the surge tank cap, fill tank, start engine, open valves, bleed heater at
                                bleeder valve.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
